title: New Mexico Resource GIS program, Dams ,New Mexico, 2007
name: New Mexico Resource GIS program, Dams ,New Mexico, 2007
description:
An inventory of the names and locations of oilfields, mines, dams, towers, and other man-made structures in New Mexico. Extracted from the USGS Geographic Names Information System.

This dataset is a subset of the original dataset which can be found with the link. This dataset only shows the features labeled with'type' = Dam.
